```php
<?php
$to = "friend@example.com";
$subject = "Greetings from me!";
$message = "Hello my brother/sister, how you dey? I just dey learn how to send email with PHP. Hope you fine!";
$headers = "From: your_email@example.com";

// Attempt to send the email
if (mail($to, $subject, $message, $headers)) {
    echo "Message don send successfully! Check your inbox.";
} else {
    echo "E no send o, try again later.";
}
?>
```

Make sure say your server dey configured well to send emails, if not e no go work. Try am small small till you get am!

